A userspace version of ipfw and dummynet, using netmap for packet I/O.
On an i7-3400, this version is able to process over 6 million packets 
per second (Mpps) with simple rulesets, and over 2.2 Mpps through 
dummynet pipes, 5..10 times faster than the in-kernel equivalent.

WWW: http://info.iet.unipi.it/~luigi/dummynet/
